{"word":"G821 - ἀτιμόω - atimóō - at-ee-mo'-o - Handle shamefully","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀτιμόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">atimóō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">at-ee-mo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Handle shamefully</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அவமானப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"to dishonor, mark with disgrace"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G820 - ἄτιμος - átimos - at'-ee-mos/820\">G820</a>; used like <a href=\"#/G818 - ἀτιμάζω - atimázō - at-im-ad'-zo/818\">G818</a>, to <i>maltreat:</i> - handle shamefully.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}